# Mg4Zn7 slab relaxation - fixed lattice, atoms free to move

units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary p p f

read_data slabs/mg4zn7_110_8layers_reconstructed_ase.data

pair_style meam
pair_coeff * * library.meam Mg Zn ZnMg.meam Zn Mg

# Output thermodynamic info every 10 steps
thermo 10
thermo_style custom step pe etotal fmax press vol

fix 1 all box/relax x 0.0 y 0.0 couple none
minimize 1e-8 1e-8 10000 100000
